
<div class="panel-group" id="accordion2">
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTen">Who, What, When, Where, Why, How</a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseTen" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <h4 class="headerunderline">Who</h4>
        <p>32 Teams may enter the Week 1 tournament of the AD2L Weekend Tournament Series (WTS)</p>
        <h4 class="headerunderline">What</h4>
        <p>The AD2L (WTS) - Captain’s Draft, Week 1</p>
        <h4 class="headerunderline">When</h4>
        <p>3 MAY 2014, @5:00pm EDT. Registration begins right away</p>
        <h4 class="headerunderline">Where</h4>
        <p>Check-in on RaidCall @4:45pm. <%=link_to "Affinity", "players/140"%> will be in the main lobby to assist you</p>
        <h4 class="headerunderline">Why</h4>
        <p>For those of us not as good as DK, we play amateur tournaments.</p>
        <h4 class="headerunderline">How</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>1. Register from your teampage.  (Can be found from the <%=link_to "My Info", (@current_user ? @current_user : "players/new")%>)</li>
          <li>2. Check-in using RaidCall by chatting with <%=link_to "Affinity", "players/140"%> in the Lounge. Say your team name and he’ll move you to the the correct bracket. </li>
          <li>3. The caster and/or admin in your bracket will create your lobby. If there is no caster and/or admin, you will simply create the lobby between the two teams</li>
          <li>4. The winner will rejoin the <b>Lounge</b> to report the win with their team name again. You will then be moved to the next bracket by <%=link_to "Affinity", "players/140"%>. </li>
          <li>5. Rinse and repeat steps 2-4 until the 1st place is yours!</li>
        <ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseEleven">RaidCall Walkthrough</a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseEleven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <ol>
          <li>1. <%=link_to "Download RaidCall", "http://www.raidcall.com/download-raidcall.html"%> (100% free)</li>
          <li>2. Create an account</li>
          <li>3. Follow this <%=link_to "link", "http://www.raidcall.com/go.php?sid=8675445&cid=1"%> or search for group [8675445], and talk to <%=link_to "Affinity", "players/140"%> in the Lounge</li>
          <li>4. DISABLE RAIDCALL’S OVERLAY FEATURE. It is incompatible with Steam’s overlay. To do this, go to > click on RaidCall icon in the top left corner > System Settings > Overlay > Change the hotkey to something you’ll never press by accident (e.g. mine is Shift+F8).</li>
        <ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
